{"tid":804672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉江華口快 黃金寶變洪金寶","createTime":"2018-09-03T07:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T10:30:31.000Z","uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b667e52286516e4bd66abb759f25528d5a262fa","tid":804672,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】由中國香港單車總會主辦、新鴻基地產贊助嘅「新地單車學院2018先導計劃」（場地單車）噚日舉行啟動禮，民政事務局長劉江華、香港單車隊前成員黃金寶等亦有出席。<span style=\"color: red;\">劉江華致辭時就話，希望唔同社會企業能夠同學校繼續合作，培訓單車新星，更指在場學生將會成為第二個「洪金寶」，令全場大笑，劉江華一時口快講錯，自己亦好快發現，立即修正番係黃金寶。</span>"},{"pid":"54c2748ffc49fce2781e6a70659575aeca8ed21b","tid":804672,"uid":125168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/650000/651501/Laukongwah_rubbishbin_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F650000%2F651501%2FLaukongwah_rubbishbin_1024.jpg&h=6b3197c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d3e44046b0f371d58dae0d1da90b868af43c1de","tid":804672,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"劉德華訓醒未"},{"pid":"7f6d7062ce11350bcbcf8ed0f1879bec94385b48","tid":804672,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"原來佢唔係啞架"},{"pid":"30aad458f875d0207c923d1d6e94d79ba1ee9d1c","tid":804672,"uid":50889,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"黃金寶：為左生活我可以忍"},{"pid":"5c9cdcfbf14f0a4cac8c936e5b6ea52453b1ca98","tid":804672,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"擺明對稿讀都讀錯<br />\n骨子裡其實支持講獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2bd800ee5a53ac83cf19fe1c1b235b57b6ef58","tid":804672,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9cdcfbf14f0a4cac8c936e5b6ea52453b1ca98","tid":804672,"uid":16676,"l